turn.2: The Bleakening "The Bleakening" is a 2017 two-part Christmas episode of the eighth season of the American animated television series "Bob's Burgers".

turn.6: The second part is the season's seventh episode and the 136th overall and was directed by Chris Song and written by Kelvin Yu.
